frames.caption: A young girl with blonde hair and a large bow stands on a path lined with trees, surrounded by fluttering butterflies. She wears a delicate pink dress and looks delighted as she clasps her hands together. The scene is bathed in warm, golden light, creating a magical atmosphere.
